ros1_dev is the high-frequency ROS1 development workspace represented by
alg_ros1_ws.

The packages under xgc2-devops/products/ros1 are the productized ROS1
packages that have been stabilized, assigned metadata, built by CI, and
published to the XGC2 APT repository.

Dependency direction:

  xgc2-devops/products/ros1 -> CI/CD -> XGC2 APT repository -> alg_ros1_ws

alg_ros1_ws should depend on released APT packages from xgc2-devops instead of
keeping duplicated source copies for stable product packages.

Use alg_ros1_ws for active development, integration experiments, and fast
iteration. Use xgc2-devops/products/ros1 for low-frequency maintenance of
deployable ROS1 packages.
